ngles\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, the 37-year-old will solely turn his focus to the men's doubles where he is playing alongside Dan Evans with the British pair drawn to face Japanese duo Taro Daniel and Kei Nishikori in the opening round.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 822, \"end\": 831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.997803650115343, \"rank\": 0.002201184452072526, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 841, \"end\": 848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9951381504576972, \"rank\": 0.0047766487295380945, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 868, \"end\": 876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.8505240376653479, \"rank\": 0.12072401893585277, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 881, \"end\": 892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taro Daniel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\"}, {\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kei Nishikori\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\", \"dbpedia\": \"http: